<seg id=1> China Will Speed Up the Construction of Personnel Market System </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News Agency, Beijing, September 1 - Organization department of Central Committee of CPC and Ministry of Personnel issued a notice a few days ago, demanding to strengthen the construction planning of personnel market, speed up the development of personnel market and promote its health development. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> The notice pointed out a general target of cultivation and development of personnel market: to realize personal free choice of jobs and unit's free selection of personnel, demand and supply of personnel to be regulated by the market, a perfect social service, a sound social security, the market will play a fundamental role in personnel resources allocation under the macro-regulation and control of the country. </seg>
<seg id=4> The near term target of cultivation and development of personnel market includes: make fundamental policies, laws and regulations for personnel market operation within recent two or three years, widely establish personnel market places in medium and big cities, set up and develop regional personnel information networks, assist development of special personnel markets, and found regional personnel markets. </seg>
<seg id=5> Before year 2000, a nationwide personnel market system will be established primarily with perfect functioning, sound mechanism, full laws and regulations, timely guidance, and thoughtful service. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=6> Organization department of Central Committee and Ministry of Personnel asked the organization and personnel departments of all levels to intensify the construction and management, study and planning of personnel market, establish a overall arrangement and practical measures for this market, adjust measures to local conditions, give guidance according to different requirements, and to found gradually a perfect personnel market system. </seg>
</p>
